{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"bb87fcb42f22a82fc69916894f3b9a7754bc3f2e5d2afc0dd788d38ecf819556","slug":"energy-management","location":"/handbook/health/energy_management.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"精力管理：防守、留白与减负","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":2}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/handbook/health/energy_management.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/handbook/health/energy_management.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"energy_management.md","url":"/energy_management-a17fedda82f2a9a06ab8d79e1c131c9d.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根据“输入防御 → 空间预留 → 过程优化 → 认知卸载”的逻辑，对这组卡片的表述进行了优化。重点在于主动构建防御机制，而非被动承受干扰。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"SlaTa9hAFi"}],"key":"GHYfo83Iu5"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"减少信息窗口以保持长时间专注","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"JXVmbj7O7Q"}],"identifier":"id","label":"减少信息窗口以保持长时间专注","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"OMFPdUrhys"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：每天被信息洪流推着走，疲惫感多源于此。想\n要长时间沉浸，就必须主动关闭不必要的“进水口”。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"U51PQPVLKo"}],"key":"PAsysVd3Ue"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：把关“输入门”。每天设定1-2小时的“无新信息时段”，只处理存量任务。平时常问：“这个窗口（通知、群聊）现在必须开着吗？”把主动关窗当作保持专注的核心手段。","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"f5AhhxMbA0"}],"key":"FwUPT2jWzG"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为“安静地创造”留出时间，哪怕只是一小段","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"CzQB4a4xZC"}],"identifier":"id","label":"为“安静地创造”留出时间，哪怕只是一小段","html_id":"id-1","implicit":true,"key":"hKHUdgtkA4"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：在碎片间隙里，心里总冒出“想安静处理点私事”的念头。这说明创造需要留白，不能被任务填满。","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"eYFCN0flnC"}],"key":"yJq0Cwc7Nu"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：主动划定“留白时段”。每天或每周固定划出一段时间（哪怕30分钟），规则只有一个：不服务于任何外部指标。只做滋养内心的事（整理日记、试错、发呆），视其为深度工作的土壤。","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"xcWnVWTwkZ"}],"key":"ikjaCOjohH"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主动寻找“手机可处理”的任务，降低对设备的依赖","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"key":"fwL6pJbp8M"}],"identifier":"id","label":"主动寻找“手机可处理”的任务，降低对设备的依赖","html_id":"id-2","implicit":true,"key":"CgPCzvnNZM"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：流程已碎片化，手机能搞定大部分轻量操作，电脑只需用于“重活”。这其实是天然的工作量调节器。","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"Jkv7iLbObP"}],"key":"azdOXy8mCV"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：用设备切换来调节节奏。开工前先筛一遍：“哪些手机能做？”优先处理这些轻量任务。把电脑留给需要深度沉浸的“重活”，并严格限制重活时长（如1-2小时），以此物理隔离压力。","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1},"end":{"line":22,"column":1}},"key":"NeWlszZYGv"}],"key":"qEYK6AlIor"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不对复杂问题贸然分拆知识领域","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1},"end":{"line":25,"column":1}},"key":"oD0Bcz0kr6"}],"identifier":"id","label":"不对复杂问题贸然分拆知识领域","html_id":"id-3","implicit":true,"key":"HI8E0ihiLW"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"发现：面对极其复杂的技术冲击，硬要拆解往往导致混乱。承认“边界不清”，把问题“挂起来”，反而能保护心智不崩溃。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"key":"rvgwzLJOIB"}],"key":"OpJeyoCeg6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以怎么用：允许问题“悬置”。遇到当下无解或边界模糊的难题，不要强迫大脑立刻计算。把它原样记入“待定清单”，明确告诉大脑：“此问题暂存，等待更多信息。”以此卸载当下的认知负荷，避免无谓的内耗。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"yjZ1PZxP6a"}],"key":"S31TYNBhiH"}],"key":"Lpe4sBLd28"}],"key":"iiq0M5YbwQ"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}